en_445266_0	Under the guidance of the General Officer Commanding, 57 Division, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya, 15 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) troops of the 573 Brigade conducted a Shramadana at Waddakachchi School on Friday (14) under the supervision of the 573 Brigade Commander, Colonel Janaka Ranasinghe.
en_445266_1	More than 30 troops, together with civilians in the area contributed to this Shramadana campaign and cleaned the school premises and its surroundings.
